abstract: Songbird is removed from Kentucky Oaks horse race because of fever.

headline.print_headline: Fever Knocks Songbird Out of Kentucky Oaks
headline.main: Fever Knocks Songbird Out of Kentucky Oaks

snippet: Songbird would have been the overwhelming favorite for the Oaks at Churchill Downs in Louisville, Ky., the day before the Kentucky Derby.
lead_paragraph: Songbird would have been the overwhelming favorite for the Oaks at Churchill Downs in Louisville, Ky., the day before the Kentucky Derby.
